ISLAMABAD, Apr 22 (APP): The National Command and Operation Centre (NCOC) on Thursday informed that a special plane of Pakistan Air Force (PAF) carrying 0.5 million doses consignment of SinoVac Vaccine had arrived at NurKhan Airbase here from China.
In a brief statement issued by the NCOC, it was added that the consignment was procured on payment.
